Big Brother Naija 2019 housemate, Elozonam has emerged winner of this week ‘Veto Power Game of Chance’. Big Brother on Sunday said the winner of the game gets the ability to save and replace a nominated housemate even if they were the ones that had been nominated. The winner also received 100 bet Naija coins. Housemates were instructed to pick numbers and stand close to a bucket. The housemate that picked the bucket with the ‘veto power emerged winner.’ After two rounds, Elozonam won the challenge. Meanwhile, Joe and Enkay were evicted during Sunday night eviction show. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.